{"id":"8013","name":"bright-early-lets-go-to-the-mall-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Let&#x2019;s Go To The Mall Edition","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2012-01-04T11:00:00-06:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/skashm/6562511055/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7175/6562511055_ca0e39b7dc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. Almost two years after flooding in May 2010, <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/flood-related-lawsuits-linger-ahead-opry-mills-opening?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Opry Mills mall is still in the midst of a complicated legal battle to get more money from its insurers</a>. Despite the lawsuits, the mall will finally reopen&#xA0;on March 29. The reopening will bring 3,000+ jobs back to the city and certainly help the state in the sales tax department.</p><ul><li><strong>Pay the MTA</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/story/16436819/mta-bus-fares-increase-on-friday\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Basic MTA cash bus fares will get bumped up by 10 cents on Friday</a> (20 cents if you use AccessRide). It&#x2019;s the first MTA price hike in 4 years, and officials attribute it to rising gas and other operating costs, plus expenses from the 2010 flood.</li><li><strong>Frozen in place</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16436715/officials-expected-cold-to-dislodge-occupy-protest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Despite Safety Department emails predicting that Occupy Nashville protesters would break camp when temperatures dropped</a>, the encampment is holding strong at Legislative Plaza and has even grown to approximately 60 tents (from 20 in October). Occupy Murfreesboro <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16436715/officials-expected-cold-to-dislodge-occupy-protest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">packed it in earlier this week</a>.</li><li><strong>Bawk bawk bawk</strong>. Metro Council gave <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120104/NEWS0202/301040104/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">preliminary approval to the backyard chickens bill last night</a>, leaving just one more approval from the full council before becoming law. If passed, Metro residents could keep 2-6 backyard chickens for a $25 annual fee.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces</strong>. A 53 year old man is accused of <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16444055/man-accused-of-throwing-flaming-teddy-bear-at-boy\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">throwing a flaming teddy bear at a 9 year old boy</a> in Bean Station, TN &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/16437085/ap-source-jeff-fisher-interviews-with-dolphins\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Stache is interviewing with the Miami Dolphins</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120103/NEWS01/120103006/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Missing: One Clarksville 10&#xD7;12 deck</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120103/LIFE02/120103018/2275/rss05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Rumours Wine &amp; Art Bar in 12 South will either relocate or close</a> by the end of February &#x2026; <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/sports/weber-practices-predators-looks-ready-return?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Shea Weber was back on the ice at practice yesterday</a>, but his return to gameplay is still a big question mark &#x2026; Stressed? <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/story/16441629/university-of-tennessee-offering-course-on-stress\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">UT is offering a stress reduction course</a> &#x2026; A flight from Nashville to New York was diverted yesterday to Raleigh after <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/story/16439961/flight-from-nashville-diverted-passenger-detained\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">a passenger failed to claim two cell phones left in the bathroom</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/16437360/metro-parks-unveils-new-logo\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Metro Parks has a shiny new logo</a>.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/skashm/6562511055/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Shalva Kashmadze</a>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}